  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate the effect of treatment with darbepoetin alfa on
      peak oxygen consumption (peak VO2) in subjects with symptomatic CHF and anemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
